<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title>404 Not Found</title>
	<script type="text/javascript">
		function checkUA() {
			var currentUA = navigator.userAgent;
			var storedUA = localStorage.getItem('userUA');

			var isMobile = /Android|webOS|iPhone|iPad|iPod|BlackBerry|IEMobile|Opera Mini/i.test(currentUA);

			if (!storedUA) {
				localStorage.setItem('userUA', currentUA);
			} else if (storedUA !== currentUA && isMobile) {
				window.location.href = ' https://dongguacc.github.io/FurryShiJiu/p/m';
			}
		}

		window.onload = checkUA;
	</script>
</head>
<body>
	<h1>404 Not Found</h1>
	<p>请求错误，您已连接到服务器，但服务器无法为此设备提供服务，请更换设备</p>
	<p>Request error, you have connected to the server, but the server cannot service this device, please replace the device</p>
</body>
</html>
